27:38.957 --> 27:41.158
Lord, why have you forsaken me?

27:42.027 --> 27:43.728
Send me

27:43.730 --> 27:45.663
an angel of mercy

27:46.164 --> 27:49.232
to vanquish that devil teacher,

27:49.234 --> 27:50.968
Jonas,

27:50.970 --> 27:53.237
who took these disgusting photos

27:54.205 --> 27:56.573
before he becomes
a worse influence

27:56.575 --> 27:58.409
on my precious daughter.

28:02.914 --> 28:04.881
-That couldn't
have been real, right?

28:04.883 --> 28:06.783
Someone's screwing
with us, right?

28:06.785 --> 28:08.452
Who do you think it is?

28:08.454 --> 28:10.587
-I honestly don't know
what to think.

28:10.989 --> 28:12.657
-Well, what does it say again?

28:12.659 --> 28:14.191
-Um...

28:15.193 --> 28:17.762
Rule 7.85b,

28:17.764 --> 28:19.396
closing the portal:

28:19.398 --> 28:22.032
Collect the following
ten monster body parts:

28:23.000 --> 28:25.068
a krivack from a

28:25.070 --> 28:27.737
J-Z-Z-X-X-S-H

28:28.339 --> 28:31.275
an A-borg from a Memoragatu;

28:31.277 --> 28:34.012
and a bunch of other words
I don't understand.

28:34.014 --> 28:35.412
-There must be
a logical explanation.

28:35.414 --> 28:37.281
There always is.

28:37.283 --> 28:39.282
-A horn came out of his head.

28:39.284 --> 28:41.085
-Yeah.

28:41.087 --> 28:43.220
Yeah, there is that.

28:43.222 --> 28:45.222
At first, I thought Pilar cyst

28:45.224 --> 28:47.024
but those don't present
like that.

28:48.560 --> 28:50.961
-What if he was
telling the truth?

28:50.963 --> 28:52.629
-But what about science?

28:52.631 --> 28:54.032
-What about everything else?

28:54.034 --> 28:56.299
-That would mean there are
actually monsters

28:56.301 --> 28:57.801
in Coppers Cove.

28:58.369 --> 28:59.804
And...

28:59.806 --> 29:01.705
it's all our fault.

29:01.707 --> 29:03.307
-And if that is true,

29:03.641 --> 29:06.643
then that means there's
something called a Tearjerker

29:06.645 --> 29:09.179
eating people's tears
and holding them hostage!

29:09.181 --> 29:12.583
[Sigh] And if somehow Tate
has been taken or hurt

29:12.585 --> 29:14.251
because of us,

29:14.652 --> 29:16.119
then I guess that means...

29:16.121 --> 29:17.955
-Oh, son of a bitch.

29:18.457 --> 29:20.457
We gotta find that asshole.

29:20.459 --> 29:21.826
How else will we know?

29:21.828 --> 29:23.260
[Thunder clap]

29:23.262 --> 29:25.128
-Ohh! My leg!

29:25.130 --> 29:26.730
-God, that smell!
Ugh, ew.

29:27.532 --> 29:29.799
<i>-VARSHIDI:
Good afternoon, Ferrets!</i>

29:29.801 --> 29:31.234
<i>I'm giving out free...</i>

29:31.236 --> 29:33.104
<i>-ASTRID: It's just
a normal school day.</i>

29:33.106 --> 29:34.605
Just like any other day.

29:34.607 --> 29:37.374
Absolutely nothing insane
happened last night.

29:38.342 --> 29:39.844
[Thud]

29:39.846 --> 29:41.378
See?
Normal.

29:42.481 --> 29:44.482
-I'm a monster hunter.

29:44.484 --> 29:46.016
What?

29:46.018 --> 29:48.385
I opened a portal.
What?

29:48.387 --> 29:50.420
Of monsters.
What?

29:50.422 --> 29:53.390
-GIRL: Have you seen Valerie?
She wasn't on the bus.

29:54.058 --> 29:56.159
-Oh, no: her allergies!
It got Val!

29:56.161 --> 29:58.061
-Let's not jump
to conclusions yet.

29:58.063 --> 29:59.797
-Okay, but what if it did?

29:59.799 --> 30:01.399
[Whoosh]

30:01.401 --> 30:02.933
[Bright upbeat music]

30:10.641 --> 30:13.176
-You know you're not as subtle
as you think you are.

30:13.178 --> 30:15.579
-Uh, uh, so you're
talking to me now?

30:15.581 --> 30:17.381
-I never didn't talk to you.

30:17.383 --> 30:18.849
-Uh, mmkay.

30:19.650 --> 30:21.785
Ever since you got cool
and I got fat,

30:21.787 --> 30:23.320
we haven't exactly been buddies.

30:23.322 --> 30:25.522
-It's not like you've given me
the time of day

30:25.524 --> 30:27.058
since Astrid came to town.

30:28.326 --> 30:30.193
So, um...

30:30.195 --> 30:31.596
do you...

30:31.598 --> 30:33.196
Do you have any leads?

30:33.198 --> 30:34.931
-Let's say, TBD.

30:34.933 --> 30:36.666
Have you heard anything
from him?

30:36.668 --> 30:37.735
-Pfft.
You tell me.

30:37.737 --> 30:40.604
You're the creeper stalking
everyone around town, right?

30:40.606 --> 30:42.339
-Right. Cool,
have a nice life.

30:43.174 --> 30:44.775
-Oh, sorry. Um...

30:45.844 --> 30:47.411
No offense.

30:49.080 --> 30:51.214
I-I heard about
the Pudge Patrol thing.

30:51.616 --> 30:53.617
I'm sure Tate didn't mean
for it to spread.

30:53.619 --> 30:55.753
-Well, as long as
he didn't mean it.

30:56.420 --> 30:57.921
-Well, I'm sorry.

31:00.124 --> 31:01.525
-So, your jerk boyfriend...

31:02.894 --> 31:05.161
Have you heard from him or what?

31:05.163 --> 31:06.831
-No. Nothing.

31:06.833 --> 31:08.298
-Crap.

31:08.300 --> 31:10.100
-You know, he's not...

31:10.102 --> 31:11.636
always an asshole.

31:12.838 --> 31:14.638
Unlike me.

31:14.640 --> 31:16.174
[Chuckling]

31:17.241 --> 31:20.077
-For those of you who signed up
for formal decorations committee

31:20.079 --> 31:21.778
because you care,

31:21.780 --> 31:23.847
very cool.
For those of you

31:23.849 --> 31:25.950
forced to sign up
because of detention, Sparrow,

31:25.952 --> 31:27.885
if you beef up my dance,
I will end you.

31:27.887 --> 31:29.519
Got it?

31:30.254 --> 31:32.656
First official meeting
is tomorrow during lunch.

31:33.392 --> 31:34.959
Don't be late.

31:35.493 --> 31:37.027
[Sucks teeth]

31:43.535 --> 31:45.503
-Oh, shit.
Tears.

31:46.270 --> 31:48.672
Yo, she-she didn't
mean anything by it.

31:48.940 --> 31:50.540
Are you crying under there?

31:50.542 --> 31:52.209
It probably doesn't matter,

31:52.211 --> 31:54.745
but maybe i-it does so stop!

31:57.148 --> 31:58.682
Just in case.

31:58.684 --> 32:00.218
[Tender music]

32:02.820 --> 32:04.254
-You're a weird girl.

32:05.289 --> 32:06.757
[Indistinct conversations]

32:13.498 --> 32:14.932
-Oh, I could just...
Uh!

32:21.606 --> 32:23.273
-Oh, hey.

32:23.275 --> 32:25.842
-I think my Sparrow deflowering
dreams are done forever.

32:25.844 --> 32:26.843
-Oh.

32:26.845 --> 32:29.046
-But I do think I've maybe
saved his life,

32:29.048 --> 32:30.447
so there's that.

32:30.449 --> 32:32.282
-Oh, no!
And... cool?

32:33.351 --> 32:36.653
So, I talked to Candace
and I kinda resolved some stuff.

32:36.655 --> 32:38.923
-Ew! You talked
to Princess Turd-vomit?

32:38.925 --> 32:40.690
How was that?

32:40.692 --> 32:42.325
- It was fine.
- Fine?

32:42.327 --> 32:43.861
- Mm-hm.
- That's it?

32:44.930 --> 32:46.529
-What is that face?

32:46.531 --> 32:48.031
-What face?

32:48.934 --> 32:50.533
[Deep bass boom]

32:50.936 --> 32:52.603
There is a weird-looking

32:52.605 --> 32:54.537
mystical golden orb in there.

32:54.539 --> 32:55.906
[Mysterious music]

32:58.342 --> 33:00.777
-Goddamn it, Unicorn Boy.

33:01.345 --> 33:02.879
Way to pile it on.

33:02.881 --> 33:04.814
Can't we just quietly
ignore this all away?

33:04.816 --> 33:06.349
-I don't think so.

33:06.351 --> 33:07.752
-Like we need another reason

33:07.754 --> 33:09.686
for people to think
we're freakshows.

33:09.688 --> 33:11.288
-You are freakshows.

33:15.559 --> 33:17.694
-Hello, monster hunters.

33:17.696 --> 33:19.229
Jesus!

33:19.231 --> 33:20.897
Use me to hold
the ten body parts

33:20.899 --> 33:22.499
needed to close the portal.

33:22.501 --> 33:24.367
-Is he frickin' serious?

33:24.369 --> 33:25.969
Step one:

33:25.971 --> 33:27.971
retrieve the Tontoom
from the Tearjerker.

33:27.973 --> 33:30.573
His body is weak,
but his urge to kill is strong.

33:30.575 --> 33:32.575
And if you haven't
figured it out yet,

33:32.577 --> 33:34.711
follow your nose and leg,

33:34.713 --> 33:37.347
AKA your monster-tracker
superpowers.

33:38.449 --> 33:41.118
I can't believe
these are the powers we get!

33:42.052 --> 33:43.521
[Intriguing music]

33:47.925 --> 33:49.460
How does it work?

33:50.861 --> 33:52.696
[Hissing]
Oh, heh-heh.

33:56.467 --> 33:58.001
-BOTH:
Time for some recon.

33:58.003 --> 33:59.537
-I'll get the car.

33:59.539 --> 34:01.071
[Exciting music]

34:02.006 --> 34:03.674
- Ugh.
- Where are we?

34:03.676 --> 34:06.243
-This is where my leg
told me to take us.

34:06.245 --> 34:07.944
-Well, what's your
leg saying now?

34:07.946 --> 34:09.413
-Cold.

34:09.814 --> 34:11.414
Cold.

34:11.416 --> 34:13.017
Warm.
[Astrid sniffs]

34:13.019 --> 34:14.684
Warmer.

34:14.686 --> 34:16.753
Hot, hot.
What's your nose saying?

34:16.755 --> 34:18.222
-Ah, same!

34:18.756 --> 34:20.524
Man, lamest powers ever.

34:21.827 --> 34:23.660
-Oh!
My leg stopped.

34:24.229 --> 34:25.762
But it's...

34:25.764 --> 34:28.431
throbbing like a mofo
from all this cramping.

34:28.433 --> 34:30.567
-I like it when you talk dirty.

34:31.168 --> 34:33.237
But yeah, same.
My nose stopped, too.

34:34.338 --> 34:36.039
-I-I need to sit down a sec.

34:36.041 --> 34:38.075
-Yeah. BRB.
I gotta pee so bad.

34:39.376 --> 34:41.712
-I'll be here, heh,
massaging myself.

34:41.714 --> 34:43.179
-Ah, yeah, get it, girl!

34:43.181 --> 34:44.781
-You know what I mean!

34:44.783 --> 34:46.250
[Sighing]

34:46.752 --> 34:48.318
Oh, okay...

34:48.986 --> 34:50.587
[Mysterious music]

34:50.589 --> 34:52.156
Ouch!

34:52.158 --> 34:53.657
Yeah, great power.

34:53.659 --> 34:55.192
Hey-hey Astrid?

34:57.661 --> 34:59.196
Hm.

35:01.632 --> 35:03.167
[Echoing sobs in distance]

35:06.037 --> 35:07.571
Astrid?

35:09.273 --> 35:11.174
-TEARJERKER:
Try again, Lilly.

35:11.676 --> 35:13.210
[Evil laughter]

35:14.413 --> 35:15.946
Well, look who it is.

35:18.417 --> 35:18.481
It's my number one
portal-opening party girl.

35:18.682 --> 35:26.682
I've been waiting to invite you

35:28.027 --> 35:29.893
to my very special party.

35:30.562 --> 35:33.029
You're not normally
invited to parties.

35:33.031 --> 35:35.298
Is that right?

35:35.300 --> 35:36.833
Oh, no.

35:36.835 --> 35:38.569
Did I hit a nerve?

35:38.571 --> 35:40.203
[Sobbing]

35:40.205 --> 35:42.906
You're not
going to cry, are you?

35:42.908 --> 35:44.241
-Please...

35:46.845 --> 35:48.378
-Let it out.

35:49.114 --> 35:50.881
[Snorts]

35:51.448 --> 35:53.116
Shit, that tastes...

35:53.118 --> 35:54.584
good!

35:54.586 --> 35:56.419
You know why?

35:56.421 --> 35:58.555
It's because you hate yourself.

35:59.124 --> 36:00.790
-Oh, no.

36:00.792 --> 36:02.225
-Sh, sh, sh, sh, sh.

36:04.395 --> 36:05.995
Now sad...

36:05.997 --> 36:07.731
it tastes good

36:07.733 --> 36:09.666
but worthless

36:09.668 --> 36:12.002
is delicious.

36:12.004 --> 36:14.037
-Well, I'm...
I'm not.

36:14.039 --> 36:15.905
-Sure you are, girlfriend.

36:16.875 --> 36:19.410
Now just give daddy
one more taste

36:19.412 --> 36:21.011
before we get started.

36:22.246 --> 36:23.781
[Squelching]

36:23.783 --> 36:25.416
[Scream]

36:25.418 --> 36:27.951
-Lilly! Get the hell away
from my friend!

36:29.020 --> 36:30.453
[Grunt]

36:30.455 --> 36:31.956
-Ooh!

36:31.958 --> 36:33.356
[Roar]

36:33.358 --> 36:34.991
Come on.
Let's go.

36:34.993 --> 36:36.626
Keep the flashlight,
tear jerk off!

36:36.628 --> 36:38.095
[Upbeat exciting music]

36:38.829 --> 36:40.364
[Laughing]

36:42.333 --> 36:43.967
[Heavy breathing]

36:44.936 --> 36:46.436
Ah, oh...

36:49.407 --> 36:50.941
Oh, my God.

36:51.775 --> 36:53.643
Lilly, are you okay?

36:53.645 --> 36:55.111
-You saved my life.

36:55.113 --> 36:57.047
-You were right:
this shit's real.

36:57.682 --> 36:59.282
Oh, crap, I'm so--

36:59.550 --> 37:01.251
I'm so glad you're okay.

37:03.120 --> 37:04.522
What?

37:04.524 --> 37:06.123
What happened back there?

37:06.125 --> 37:07.791
You seem...

37:07.793 --> 37:09.259
so sad.

37:09.261 --> 37:10.727
-It was awful.

37:11.662 --> 37:13.163
He told me the truth...

37:14.198 --> 37:15.733
What I already knew.

37:16.066 --> 37:17.601
That I'm worthless.

37:17.603 --> 37:19.135
-Lilly,

37:19.137 --> 37:22.071
you are the farthest thing
from worthless.

37:22.073 --> 37:24.874
You're the most
important person in my life.

37:24.876 --> 37:26.275
-Then why do people
keep telling it to me

37:26.277 --> 37:27.777
if it's not true?

37:27.779 --> 37:29.679
-Because some people are idiots!

37:30.448 --> 37:33.217
And that thing's
a literal monster.

37:33.219 --> 37:34.884
[Tender music]

37:35.552 --> 37:37.887
You were the only one
smart enough to see

37:37.889 --> 37:39.655
what was actually happening.

37:40.557 --> 37:42.692
And who could be worthless
with such a badass

37:42.694 --> 37:44.161
leg cramp superpower?

37:44.561 --> 37:46.030
Huh?

37:54.573 --> 37:57.908
Now, how do we kill this psycho
butt-face monster thing?

37:57.910 --> 37:59.510
-Okay.

37:59.512 --> 38:01.044
[Upbeat music]

38:02.480 --> 38:03.980
Okay.

38:03.982 --> 38:05.516
Ten monster body parts...

38:06.583 --> 38:08.417
place them in orb...

38:08.419 --> 38:09.920
yada, yada, yada...

38:09.922 --> 38:11.454
Um...

38:11.456 --> 38:12.990
Tearjerker!
Found it.

38:14.124 --> 38:15.859
Okay, listen to this.

38:17.361 --> 38:19.195
-Cut out his Tontoom,

38:19.730 --> 38:23.000
permeate him
with Krontoxix cocktail.

38:23.600 --> 38:25.335
[Sighs]
Cool.

38:25.337 --> 38:26.604
Yeah, easy peasy.

38:26.606 --> 38:28.237
Clear as day.

38:28.239 --> 38:29.806
-I see you found what I left
in your mailbox.

38:29.808 --> 38:31.407
-Oh!

38:31.409 --> 38:32.942
It's called a locker

38:32.944 --> 38:35.012
and it's extremely public.

38:35.014 --> 38:37.948
How do you expect us to keep
a low profile about all this?

38:37.950 --> 38:39.482
-Oh, you'd be surprised.

38:39.484 --> 38:41.150
People see what they wanna see.

38:41.152 --> 38:43.086
Most people, you know,
just forget,

38:43.088 --> 38:44.888
or they'll invent
their own explanation.

38:45.222 --> 38:47.558
Anyway, I just came
to bring you this.

38:47.560 --> 38:49.692
It'll take
the Tearjerker right out.

38:49.694 --> 38:52.829
You ran away
before I could give it to you.

38:52.831 --> 38:55.298
Just mix it in
with some stolen victim tears

38:55.300 --> 38:57.166
and some elephant tranquilizer.

38:57.168 --> 38:58.868
-Where are we gonna get
elephant tra--?

39:01.038 --> 39:03.039
And you're sure he has Tate?

39:03.041 --> 39:05.174
And Valerie and the woman
who went missing?

39:05.176 --> 39:06.976
-Yes.

39:06.978 --> 39:08.978
Usually distills his victims
for 48 hours

39:08.980 --> 39:10.446
before he kills them.

39:11.316 --> 39:14.483
To-to wring out
as much despair as possible.

39:14.485 --> 39:16.085
Hm.

39:16.087 --> 39:18.621
For when he drains
and drinks the bodily fluids.

39:18.623 --> 39:20.257
Friends, come on. I...

39:20.259 --> 39:21.858
-Oh!

39:22.392 --> 39:24.794
-Anyway, you have about...

39:24.796 --> 39:26.929
eight hours left to get to them.

39:27.531 --> 39:30.499
And remember: if you don't get
the Tontoom,

39:30.501 --> 39:32.001
then you can't close the portal

39:32.003 --> 39:33.403
and if you can't
close the portal

39:33.405 --> 39:34.838
then the world just...

39:35.272 --> 39:36.873
[Pops lips]

39:36.875 --> 39:38.542
Dies.

39:40.945 --> 39:42.645
Good luck!

39:42.647 --> 39:44.513
-But, wait!
What's a Tontoom?

39:44.515 --> 39:45.982
[Frustrated sigh]

39:53.457 --> 39:54.958
-Hey, Astrid!

39:54.960 --> 39:56.659
-What?

39:56.661 --> 39:58.661
-Got a little
something in your hair.

39:59.631 --> 40:01.231
Is that blood?

40:02.300 --> 40:03.699
-Um...

40:03.701 --> 40:05.168
I think so.

40:05.170 --> 40:06.836
-Cool.

40:06.838 --> 40:08.305
[Bright music]

40:09.973 --> 40:11.474
[Funky electro music]

40:12.843 --> 40:14.411
[Astrid laughs]

40:29.259 --> 40:30.860
<i>♪♪ We ferocious ♪♪</i>

40:31.262 --> 40:32.895
[Electro music ends abruptly]

40:33.297 --> 40:35.064
-Let's do this.

40:35.066 --> 40:36.833
-Oh, my God, this is insane.

40:38.068 --> 40:40.736
I honestly don't know
if I can do this, Astrid.

40:40.738 --> 40:42.506
-You are stronger
than you think.

40:42.508 --> 40:44.007
-Oh...

40:44.009 --> 40:45.409
I'm scared.

40:45.411 --> 40:47.810
- I'm right behind you.
- Okay.

40:47.812 --> 40:49.412
-Just you and me, Lils.

40:49.414 --> 40:52.415
Hey, we're the only ones
who can save the world.

40:52.417 --> 40:53.883
Just us.

40:54.652 --> 40:57.020
It's kinda cool
when you think about it.

40:57.022 --> 40:59.556
-Maybe being us
ain't so bad after all.

40:59.558 --> 41:01.124
-Hm.

41:02.092 --> 41:03.560
-Pudge Patrol:

41:03.562 --> 41:06.530
armed and ready
for some mega ass-kicking.

41:06.532 --> 41:08.431
-Oh, my God!
Pudge Patrol!

41:08.433 --> 41:11.034
Takin' it back!
You're a genius!

41:12.670 --> 41:14.237
[Crying]

41:14.239 --> 41:16.439
-TATE:
Help! Help.

41:16.441 --> 41:18.307
Help!

41:18.309 --> 41:19.876
[Sobbing]

41:20.777 --> 41:22.511
[Tearjerker vocalizing
excitedly]

41:22.513 --> 41:24.447
[Upbeat techno music]

41:24.449 --> 41:26.382
-Ah, ooh, uh!

41:26.384 --> 41:27.884
-Okay.

41:31.388 --> 41:32.923
Let's do this.

41:32.925 --> 41:34.491
Okay.

41:40.464 --> 41:42.131
Love you.

41:42.133 --> 41:43.566
[Sobbing continues]

41:44.102 --> 41:45.669
Good luck.

41:50.007 --> 41:51.474
[Tearjerker laughs]

41:51.476 --> 41:53.610
- Hey, Jerkface, wanna go again?

41:53.612 --> 41:55.745
-A return guest!

41:56.747 --> 41:58.214
My favourite!

42:00.350 --> 42:01.784
[Whimpering]

42:02.153 --> 42:03.487
-Sh-sh-sh.

42:03.489 --> 42:05.055
-Welcome...

42:05.789 --> 42:07.257
to the paaartyyy!

42:12.296 --> 42:13.630
You poor thing...

42:14.331 --> 42:16.032
Don't you know

42:16.034 --> 42:18.702
faking confidence
doesn't make you any less...

42:19.637 --> 42:21.204
worthless?

42:22.606 --> 42:24.107
[Squelching]

42:27.578 --> 42:29.178
-Astrid!
Now!

42:29.180 --> 42:30.346
-Taste this!

42:30.348 --> 42:31.881
-Ah!

42:31.883 --> 42:33.250
[Sizzling]

42:34.851 --> 42:36.320
[Gagging]

42:37.354 --> 42:38.788
-Whoa.

42:41.458 --> 42:43.059
-I think it's stopping.

42:43.061 --> 42:45.929
-Let's dissect this mofo
and get the hell outta here!

42:46.797 --> 42:48.131
[Squelching]

42:49.266 --> 42:50.800
[Exploding innards]

42:51.068 --> 42:52.935
-Uh, gross!

42:52.937 --> 42:55.004
-Is this it?
[Squelching]

42:55.006 --> 42:56.539
-Oh, you know what?

42:56.541 --> 42:58.541
I think "Tontoom"
basically means tongue.

42:58.543 --> 43:00.142
-Ha!

43:00.144 --> 43:01.677
I got it!

43:01.679 --> 43:03.279
-Okay.

43:03.281 --> 43:04.748
-Ugh.

43:05.883 --> 43:07.317
-Ew...

43:07.951 --> 43:09.552
-Ugh.

43:09.554 --> 43:11.288
-Oh, look on the bright side:

43:11.290 --> 43:13.824
only nine more of these
and we can close the portal.

43:13.826 --> 43:16.226
-Oh, great.
Just in time for Formal.

43:16.228 --> 43:17.761
[Laughter]

43:19.229 --> 43:20.563
[Screaming]

43:20.565 --> 43:22.064
[Sobbing]

43:22.066 --> 43:23.300
-Look out!

43:23.302 --> 43:25.034
[Growling]

43:25.869 --> 43:27.370
-TEARJERKER:
Astrid...

43:27.805 --> 43:32.041
I can see why your mom
is so deeply ashamed of you.

43:32.043 --> 43:34.777
Always ruining everything.

43:34.779 --> 43:36.012
-LILLY: Go hide
over here.

43:36.014 --> 43:40.249
-Pitiful. I'm going to put you
out of your misery right now!

43:40.251 --> 43:42.451
-Wait!
Some party.

43:42.453 --> 43:44.120
All your snacks are gone.

43:44.122 --> 43:45.622
[Tense music]

43:47.057 --> 43:49.125
Who's the sad one now?

43:49.127 --> 43:50.860
[Chemical hissing]
[Roar]

43:50.862 --> 43:52.062
[Thudding to ground]

43:53.997 --> 43:55.531
[Explosive breath]

43:55.533 --> 43:57.099
-I've officially decided

43:57.534 --> 43:59.335
parties are overrated.

43:59.337 --> 44:01.137
[Astrid and Lilly
sobbing in relief]

44:04.409 --> 44:05.941
Okay. Come on.

44:05.943 --> 44:07.743
-I'm dehydrated.

44:07.745 --> 44:10.479
-ASTRID: Yeah, don't got
no water right now.

44:10.481 --> 44:11.947
[Unintelligible whispers]

44:12.417 --> 44:13.949
Okay, we'll get you water.

44:13.951 --> 44:15.551
- Ow!
- Oh, sorry.

44:15.553 --> 44:17.286
-Are you okay?

44:17.288 --> 44:18.621
-I don't know.

44:18.623 --> 44:20.223
What just happened?
Wh-what was that? Was...

44:20.225 --> 44:21.625
Was that a monster?!

44:21.627 --> 44:23.759
-Look, it's a long story,

44:23.761 --> 44:25.995
but right now we just need
to get you and Val home, okay?

44:25.997 --> 44:28.231
I'll explain on the way.
- Who's Val?

44:28.233 --> 44:30.433
-She goes to school with us.

44:31.102 --> 44:32.968
She was at your party!

44:32.970 --> 44:34.003
-Really?

44:34.005 --> 44:37.306
-Maybe you need to
get your head out of your ass.

44:37.308 --> 44:38.575
-I don't know what to say.

44:38.577 --> 44:40.943
-You can start by thanking us,

44:41.578 --> 44:43.112
Pudge Patrol,

44:43.114 --> 44:45.848
for drowning in monster guts
to save your life!

44:45.850 --> 44:47.383
-Pudge Patrol.

44:47.385 --> 44:48.951
We're takin' it back!

44:48.953 --> 44:50.319
Oh, and, uh, don't worry,

44:50.321 --> 44:52.655
we won't tell anyone
about us rescuing you.

44:52.657 --> 44:53.723
In fact, we probably

44:53.725 --> 44:56.058
shouldn't talk about this to,
like, anyone.

44:56.060 --> 44:57.394
-Yeah, cover story.
Good idea.

44:57.396 --> 44:58.661
- Right?
- Mm-hm.

44:58.663 --> 45:00.063
-Yeah, sure.

45:00.065 --> 45:01.797
Nobody would believe
monsters are real.

45:01.799 --> 45:03.399
Or that I spent
more than five minutes

45:03.401 --> 45:05.568
with you dorks, anyway,
so we're cool.

45:06.403 --> 45:07.837
-Hm.

45:08.972 --> 45:10.407
-Also, thanks.

45:11.341 --> 45:12.975
-Oh, my God!
Oh, my God!

45:12.977 --> 45:14.443
Monster!

45:16.146 --> 45:18.247
-Oops.
Just a shadow.

45:24.554 --> 45:26.356
-I had the weirdest dream

45:26.358 --> 45:29.091
that I was in a drug den
with a sexy monster.

45:29.093 --> 45:30.559
-Your mind, Val!

45:30.561 --> 45:32.095
[Snapping fingers]

45:36.166 --> 45:38.802
-You guys chose a dumb theme
for the dance,

45:38.804 --> 45:40.503
even though I asked you not to.

45:40.505 --> 45:42.171
So, I chose something new.

45:42.640 --> 45:45.942
I am super stoked to announce
the new cool theme:

45:46.811 --> 45:48.512
Angels & Demons!

45:48.514 --> 45:50.046
-A little on the nose.

45:50.048 --> 45:51.247
-And now...

45:51.249 --> 45:53.850
I would like to
welcome back to Pine

45:53.852 --> 45:56.252
your favourite ferret:

45:56.254 --> 45:58.388
Tate Hudson!

45:58.390 --> 46:00.556
-Ah-ha-ha-ha!

46:00.558 --> 46:01.992
What's up?
What's up?

46:01.994 --> 46:03.692
-VARSHIDI:
He's alive, guys! Yeah!

46:03.694 --> 46:05.195
-Okay, thanks, guys.

46:05.197 --> 46:07.263
Super stoked to be back here.

46:07.265 --> 46:09.865
A-a quick reminder
to everybody, all right?

46:09.867 --> 46:11.735
Wear a helmet
before you go bouldering!

46:11.737 --> 46:13.203
You won't regret that, okay.

46:13.205 --> 46:14.737
[Laughs]

46:14.739 --> 46:16.572
-I do have somebody to thank.

46:16.574 --> 46:18.073
[Tender music]

46:18.075 --> 46:20.477
I could not have done it
without them.

46:22.412 --> 46:24.514
Candy, baby,
will you come up here?

46:24.516 --> 46:26.048
[Music fades out]

46:28.619 --> 46:30.352
Thank you.
[Cheers and applause]

46:31.087 --> 46:32.556
-I guess some things
never change.

46:33.357 --> 46:35.424
-Some stuff changes!

46:35.426 --> 46:37.227
Like, I guess monsters are real.

46:37.627 --> 46:39.395
-I guess we're
monster hunters now.

46:40.698 --> 46:42.999
Arguably cooler
than iguanas and SNFU.

46:43.367 --> 46:46.168
-I'm gonna get so much ass
it's gonna be freaky.

46:46.170 --> 46:47.670
-You guys are freaky.

46:49.306 --> 46:50.939
-Damn right we are!

46:50.941 --> 46:52.709
[Laughing]
[Theme music]

46:52.711 --> 46:54.343
[Soft boom]
[Tense music]

46:54.345 --> 46:55.845
[Crickets chirping]

46:59.082 --> 47:00.649
-Hello?

47:00.651 --> 47:02.084
[Clattering]

47:02.887 --> 47:05.254
Jamison, if that is you

47:05.256 --> 47:07.523
playing another
one of your pranks,

47:07.525 --> 47:10.125
then I will be forced
to tell your mo--

47:10.127 --> 47:11.727
[Sharp inhale and exhale]

47:11.729 --> 47:13.229
[Quiet tense music]

47:15.799 --> 47:17.934
Mighty Lord and Savior,

47:20.070 --> 47:21.571
you have chosen me!

47:24.541 --> 47:27.844
What an unusual-looking
angel of his mercy!

47:29.746 --> 47:31.881
Not at all
what I expected, but...

47:33.483 --> 47:34.917
no matter.

47:36.220 --> 47:38.054
You heard my prayers.

47:38.888 --> 47:40.957
And you are here to rid me

47:41.625 --> 47:43.960
of that evil teacher,

47:44.428 --> 47:45.895
Jonas.

47:47.364 --> 47:48.798
[Menacing music]

47:49.900 --> 47:51.434
-VOICE:
I am here

47:51.702 --> 47:53.269
to serve.

47:56.073 --> 47:57.640
[Closing theme]
